{"tid":1412350,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓國瑜突現身「支持民主自由」 促港府成立獨立調查委員會","createTime":"2019-08-05T06:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-07T13:11:16.000Z","uid":212249,"like":12,"dislike":756,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"20a8b3984cdb90a918ae9cbe4299666f4b4d62be","tid":1412350,"uid":212249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:19:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190805/large/1564980019_350f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190805%2Flarge%2F1564980019_350f.jpg&h=eb07b431&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n港府拒絕回應對修訂《逃犯條例》相關訴求，引發全港大罷工。台灣高雄市長韓國瑜今早原取消既定行程，臨時又於上午11時10分接受媒體訪問，被問及「香港大罷工」時，他說，香港跟台灣一水之隔，站在台灣立場，一定支持香港的民主自由，他還向港府喊話：「必須迅速成立獨立調查委員會，如果香港動亂持續下去，不光是香港的損失，也會是台灣重大的損失！」<br />\n<br />\n香港今日發起大罷工，韓國瑜被媒體問及此事，顯然是因有前車之鑑，有好好掌握訊息，不再以「我不知道」、「我不清楚」回應，他說：「香港跟台灣的一水之隔，那我相信站在台灣的立場，一定支持香港的民主自由，希望香港能趕快重新恢復繁榮、穩定、和諧。」<br />\n韓國瑜認為，從反送中到大罷工，香港政府跟香港市民之間對立急遽升高，「我覺得香港政府必須迅速成立獨立調查委員會，把這幾件暴力的事件，能夠做一個清楚的調查，成立獨立調查委員會，對現階段來說，緩和香港市民的情緒，也會有所幫助。」<br />\n<br />\n韓國瑜並指出，香港跟台灣之間的貿易、旅遊來往非常頻繁，「如果香港動亂持續下去，不光是香港的損失，也會是台灣重大的損失，所以我們希望香港政府要趕快勇於成立獨立調查委員會，而且一定要公正的、客觀的來做一個最真實的一個調查，台灣人民都非常關心香港這一次大罷工的事件。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190805/59898524?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2F2szPUMkCyRPzNuvIjdPaXfxkCoaneFxPGx-G9kH53wR6FvhvQvj-06I\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190805%2F59898524%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2F2szPUMkCyRPzNuvIjdPaXfxkCoaneFxPGx-G9kH53wR6FvhvQvj-06I&d=7QdSi1Eq0NVbLWVUesVCWFznTIwtKWugEfQLgcbUzc4%3D&h=a2636a75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190805%2F59898524%3Futm_campaign%3Dhkad_social_hk.nextmedia%26utm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook%26utm_content%3Dlink_post%26fbclid%3DIwAR2F2szPUMkCyRPzNuvIjdPaXfxkCoaneFxPGx-G9kH53wR6FvhvQvj-06I&h=d1a8d3a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20190805/59898524?utm_campaign=hkad_social_hk.nextmedia&amp;utm_medium=social&amp;utm_source=facebook&amp;utm_content=link_post&amp;fbclid=IwAR2F2szPUMkCyRPzNuvIjdPaXfxkCoaneFxPGx-G9kH53wR6FvhvQvj-06I</a>"},{"pid":"907f08f946f90ebaa9a5fbee4fb8bfbd8321b8d4","tid":1412350,"uid":266683,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:20:37.000Z","msg":"拯救香港，落實真普選！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1411693\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1411693</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"8a2a508affcec44d5b508c516596670d721b078c","tid":1412350,"uid":41245,"like":401,"dislike":4,"score":397,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:21:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n俾你林鄭搞死啦<br />\n依家我選唔到俾支共清算呀"},{"pid":"98f26fa3e7065b4d0bc1e35313e5008e29092392","tid":1412350,"uid":171399,"like":212,"dislike":4,"score":208,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:22:21.000Z","msg":"又係講錢。。。 大佬呀 我地家陣係爭取自由民主呀"},{"pid":"9153e06795ee6223e048b46ba46d34f01879c6ff","tid":1412350,"uid":3241,"like":203,"dislike":4,"score":199,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:22:41.000Z","msg":"你驚自己選唔撚到炸"},{"pid":"69768a2ec32204026246ee2253d7913393d88e04","tid":1412350,"uid":261914,"like":205,"dislike":3,"score":202,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:23:19.000Z","msg":"為選票真係咩大話都講得出口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c8c773bf3bd6e02158ef0353752b86acb0ca4a0","tid":1412350,"uid":262249,"like":102,"dislike":5,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T06:23:57.000Z","msg":"洗